<div class="why">
  <h2>What we stand for</h2>
  <div class="why-cards-container container">
    <div class="row">
      <div id="why-card-1" class="why-card card-become-helpr col-4" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000">
        <h3>Reducing inequalities</h3>
        <p>Helpr is one answer to some of society's challenges like poverty or the environment. We believe that we can make things better by helping others, sharing, and wanting to improve living conditions in our society. </p>
      </div>

      <div id="why-card-2" class="why-card card-need-help col-4" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1000">
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <p>More and more people live in poverty and in unstable situations. By relying on the generosity of its users, Helpr contributes to a collaborative system based on exchange and mutual support. Helpr is also a great way to meet the people around you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div id="showcase-helprs">
  <h2>Top Helprs</h2>
  <div class="row cards-showcase justify-content-center " data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1000">
  <% @top_users.each do |user| %>
    <%= link_to user_path(user), class:"text-decoration-none" do %>
      <div class="card-helpr col-2">
        <% if  user.photo.attached? %>
          <%= cl_image_tag user.photo.key, height: 104, :quality=>60, crop: :mfit, class: "avatar-xxl", alt: "profile image"  %>
        <% else %>
          <div class="avatar-xxl">
            <%= cl_image_tag("fpatfvf9edoaaqhbkfrt",
                   width: 104, crop: :fill, class: "avatar-xxl", alt: "profile image")  %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        <p><%= user.first_name %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

